State of Connecticut v. Jamie Scott (11848)

Dupont, C. J., Lavery and Heiman, Js.

Argued October 28 decision released November 23, 1993 Stephen V. Moran, assistant public defender, for the appellant (defendant). Nancy L. Gillespie, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, was Herbert E. Carlson, supervisory assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
